## 1. PROJECT SUMMARY

| Field | Detail |
|---|---|
| **Project Name** | `nursing-rag-frontend` |
| **Type** | Single-Page Web Application (SPA) — Frontend only |
| **Purpose** | A ChatGPT-style AI learning assistant UI for Nursing and Pharmacy students, supporting a Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) backend |
| **Current State** | **Demo/Prototype** — authentication is mocked (no real API calls), AI responses are simulated with `setTimeout`, no backend integration exists yet |
| **Primary Language** | JavaScript (JSX) |
| **Version** | 0.0.0 (pre-release) |

The application presents a polished, two-panel SaaS-style interface. Users can log in or sign up (mock only), then access a workspace with a sidebar for projects/chat history, a dashboard home, and an AI chat screen.

