## 8. SECURITY OBSERVATIONS

| Severity | Issue | Location | Detail |
|---|---|---|---|
| 🟡 Medium | **No authentication guard** | `App.jsx` | `/workspace` route is publicly accessible without any session check. Anyone can navigate to `/workspace` directly. |
| 🟡 Medium | **No input validation** | `Login.jsx`, `Signup.jsx` | Form inputs are **uncontrolled** — no state tracking, no sanitization, no client-side validation beyond HTML `required`. |
| 🟡 Medium | **Broken post-login redirect** | `Login.jsx` | `navigate('/')` routes to an undefined path. Real users would land on a blank page post-login. |
